getDescription().Description: Gets the string describing the error. Descriptions are localized, and thus can be used for communicating the problem to the user.

Returns: The error code of the error
getErrorCode().Description: Gets the error code of the error. The code corresponds to one of the ERROR_* constants in @B_android#webkit#WebViewClient_E@.

ClassDesc: Encapsulates information about errors occured during loading of web resources. See @B_android#webkit#WebViewClient#onReceivedError_E@
